        "name": "🏠 BDS API - Full Documentation (2026-01-28)",
        "description": "# 📱 API Hệ Thống Quản Lý Bất Động Sản\r\n\r\n## 🔐 Authentication\r\n\r\n### API Key (Required for ALL requests)\r\n```\r\nX-API-KEY: bds-TTMIxTtE1H6MXIypiiBoa1IfpPA3D0Nb\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Bearer Token (Protected endpoints)\r\n```\r\nAuthorization: Bearer {access_token}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 📍 URLs\r\n- **Dev:** `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`\r\n- **Prod:** `https://api.yourdomain.com/v1`\r\n\r\n## 🧪 Test Accounts\r\n- Admin: `admin@example.com` / `password`\r\n- Manager: `manager@example.com` / `password`\r\n- Staff: `staff1@example.com` / `password`\r\n\r\n## 📊 Statistics\r\n- **Total Endpoints:** 43+\r\n- **Avec Auth:** 7\r\n- **Properties:** 7\r\n- **Posts:** 6\r\n- **Admin:** 14\r\n\r\n## 💡 Code Generation\r\nClick nút **Code** (`</>`) ở mỗi request để xem examples cho:\r\n- cURL, JavaScript, Python, PHP, Dart, Swift, Kotlin\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Quick Start\r\n1. Import collection\r\n2. Send **Login** → Token auto-saved\r\n3. Test other endpoints",
